listing_company_name: Boutique Estate Agency Pty Ltd - DANDENONG NORTH
description:
This two bedroom townhouse is positioned in one of the most sought after pockets that Doveton has to offer. Architecturally designed, this home caters for all first home buyers, astute investors, and downsizers. Offering a fantastic layout and highlighted by a spacious open plan kitchen, meals and living area. Upstairs consists of two spacious bedrooms with built in robes and a central bathroom with separate toilet. Outside is the ultimate in low maintenance entertaining with a wonderful decking.

Additional Features include:
New kitchen with stainless steel appliances and ample cupboard space
Walk in robe in master bedroom
Multiple reverse cycle air conditioning units
Electric roller shutters throughout
Lock up garage with remote access and internal access
Downstairs guest powder room

Conveniently located, near Robinson Reserve, Autumn Place shopping precinct, Doveton Library, Holy Family School, Doveton College, the South Gippsland Freeway with central Dandenong within minutes.

* Photo ID is to be presented upon inspection.
* Please note that every care has been taken to verify the accuracy of the details of this advertisement, however we cannot guarantee its correctness. Prospective purchasers are requested to take such action as is necessary, to satisfy themselves of any pertinent matters.
